ruby_throat <- rth_all %>%
  mutate(Date = parse_date_time(Date, orders = c("mdy", "ydm", "dmy"))) %>%
  mutate(Year = year(Date)) %>%
  mutate(year_day = yday(Date))

rth_early <- ruby_throat %>%
  filter(Year %in% c(2010, 2011, 2012, 2013, 2014, 2015))

rth_early_25 <- rth_early %>%
  filter(Latitude > 25 & Latitude < 30) %>%
  mutate(mean = mean(year_day))

rth_early_30 <- rth_early %>%
  filter(Latitude > 30 & Latitude < 35) %>%
  mutate(mean = mean(year_day))

rth_early_35 <- rth_early %>%
  filter(Latitude > 35 & Latitude < 40) %>%
  mutate(mean = mean(year_day))

rth_early_40 <- rth_early %>%
  filter(Latitude > 40 & Latitude < 45) %>%
  mutate(mean = mean(year_day))
